{"tid":197725,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"綜援 衰仔紙?","createTime":"2017-04-12T05:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T06:28:40.000Z","uid":38745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"07a2fdcdd6eb9c0c7746bb8f66dc6e12c3e17783","tid":197725,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"討論+學術研究<br />\n<br />\n政府取消咗衰仔紙 話不與子女同住嘅長者唔需要再交衰仔紙<br />\n<br />\n咁如果係2個老人家一齊住 子女唔同佢哋住 但又有俾錢供養父母呢?<br />\n<br />\n我1823問過 我問兩老同住但子女唔同佢哋住係咪唔駛交衰仔紙 佢話:可以咁講<br />\n<br />\n但係South China Morning Post話:<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/131127_5f768228b9dfd59def711b2226235e90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F131127_5f768228b9dfd59def711b2226235e90.jpg&h=e0c9d5e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但長者要自己declare自己無仔女養 咁其實即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一齊討論吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6657363b5be48b957ff541a6aac35d8d28ae4586","tid":197725,"uid":98197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:17:53.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伸利 想知"},{"pid":"8966226d419ea8f7cdd062ee5c07d177e3811f2d","tid":197725,"uid":75541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:24:19.000Z","msg":"以前衰仔紙由子女做聲明話自己唔養老豆老母，依家變咗係兩老交張經濟援助聲明要政府養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 9up"},{"pid":"76a394ed8dde3d04fea9290494a5f5a0c9035558","tid":197725,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:36:09.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfbe1ef06a005ed8a7527e0671878d08acc60b9","tid":197725,"uid":62384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"衰仔紙係俾父母申請公屋用的"},{"pid":"9cefec1646f7f70c5f9feee3c1d6c51c047c2415","tid":197725,"uid":22477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:19:56.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"961253d97a9f2203378cb8c67b64d5bc0d48aaa9","tid":197725,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前衰仔紙由子女做聲明話自己唔養老豆老母，依家變咗係兩老交張經濟援助聲明要政府養<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 9up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁理解 但就唔多明個意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f0a5374ed7218efbbdaa790b7511b03f98013f","tid":197725,"uid":38745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:23:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>衰仔紙係俾父母申請公屋用的</blockquote><br />\n綜援都要啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (以前?)"},{"pid":"9d52059c8502828561b285a7a68d8fd8a9ce0483","tid":197725,"uid":92976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"不供養父母聲明書--即係法律上子女單方面不供養父母<br />\n<br />\n咁綜緩取消長者需要尼份文件，係方便無再同住好多年既長者同啲無聯繫既子女要求簽文件。<br />\n<br />\n同住既就唔符合（因為綜緩包括左住屋津貼）<br />\n而供養果部分其實唔係銀行過數 現兜兜咁比錢父母飲茶就查唔到既。<br />\n<br />\n基本上。同申請公屋無關係。"}]}